{"tid":1460394,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國泰員工對機場手足建議","createTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T03:11:16.000Z","uid":44646,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32dde415566deb2d4e49270df4acd2058c9d29ba","tid":1460394,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yx9xQG6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYx9xQG6.jpg&h=5ef2498d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家似乎開唔到新A/C，代任職機場多年既老友POST<br />\n希望入機場手足留意<br />\n<br />\n1.唔好大安旨意，以為尋日無事，黑警無清場，<br />\n今日、明日一樣無事。<br />\n尋日大家有經驗，幾千人要由機場走<br />\n係好困難既事<br />\n黑警要封場，手足走唔到，就會大量被捕<br />\n<br />\n2.機場有秘密通道，平時官員都係由此出閘<br />\n官方可以安排抵港旅客在此通關離開<br />\n所以大家見到仍有機來港，<br />\n都不一定代表會有旅客在T1/T2出閘<br />\n黑警可能安排佢地由密道走，再在大堂拉手足<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家唔好去，建議大家小心，勿輕敵。"},{"pid":"8228f2b8a3bc755e33974a71568455366531f448","tid":1460394,"uid":53233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:45:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1961e1fbab4ff5967861bf3cbaf82f421da54dde","tid":1460394,"uid":256594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:45:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b8190af0b6aa3487709855e07ebbf2d39b4068b","tid":1460394,"uid":146118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ce542d8a497066c6c9bb448918acc48bf1c418","tid":1460394,"uid":243348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"84ee199db3a6f2e85e0f7e18b668e88d4a6b28fc","tid":1460394,"uid":249187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:48:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f75eef98acc5cc5c3b3040627260fd0013e0a6d","tid":1460394,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"721 <br />\n811"},{"pid":"cb8f4244e361d7221bfd0ce